verses.text_plain: Then came the daughters of Zelophehad, the son of Hepher, the son of Gilead, the son of Machir, the son of Manasseh, of the families of Manasseh the son of Joseph: and these are the names of his daughters; Mahlah, Noah, and Hoglah, and Milcah, and Tirzah.
verses.verse_html: 1Then came the daughters of Zelophehad, the son of Hepher, the son of Gilead, the son of Machir, the son of Manasseh, of the families of Manasseh the son of Joseph: and these are the names of his daughters; Mahlah, Noah, and Hoglah, and Milcah, and Tirzah.

verses.text_plain: And they stood before Moses, and before Eleazar the priest, and before the princes and all the congregation, by the door of the tabernacle of the congregation, saying,
verses.verse_html: 2And they stood before Moses, and before Eleazar the priest, and before the princes and all the congregation, by the door of the tabernacle of the congregation, saying,

verses.text_plain: Our father died in the wilderness, and he was not in the company of them that gathered themselves together against the Lord in the company of Korah; but died in his own sin, and had no sons.
verses.verse_html: 3Our father died in the wilderness, and he was not in the company of them that gathered themselves together against the Lord in the company of Korah; but died in his own sin, and had no sons.

tokens.text: of them that gathered themselves together

verses.text_plain: Why should the name of our father be done away from among his family, because he hath no son? Give unto us therefore a possession among the brethren of our father.
verses.verse_html:
4Why should the name of our father be done away from among his family, because he hath no son? Give unto us therefore a possession among the brethren of our father. ▼
▼ done…: Heb. diminished

verses.text_plain: And Moses brought their cause before the Lord.
verses.verse_html: 5And Moses brought their cause before the Lord.

verses.text_plain: And the Lord spake unto Moses, saying,
verses.verse_html: 6And the Lord spake unto Moses, saying,

verses.text_plain: The daughters of Zelophehad speak right: thou shalt surely give them a possession of an inheritance among their father’s brethren; and thou shalt cause the inheritance of their father to pass unto them.
verses.verse_html: 7The daughters of Zelophehad speak right: thou shalt surely give them a possession of an inheritance among their father’s brethren; and thou shalt cause the inheritance of their father to pass unto them.

tokens.text: and thou shalt cause the inheritance

verses.text_plain: And thou shalt speak unto the children of Israel, saying, If a man die, and have no son, then ye shall cause his inheritance to pass unto his daughter.
verses.verse_html: 8And thou shalt speak unto the children of Israel, saying, If a man die, and have no son, then ye shall cause his inheritance to pass unto his daughter.

tokens.text: then ye shall cause his inheritance

verses.text_plain: And if he have no daughter, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his brethren.
verses.verse_html: 9And if he have no daughter, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his brethren.

tokens.text: And if he have no daughter

verses.text_plain: And if he have no brethren, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his father’s brethren.
verses.verse_html: 10And if he have no brethren, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his father’s brethren.

verses.text_plain: And if his father have no brethren, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his kinsman that is next to him of his family, and he shall possess it: and it shall be unto the children of Israel a statute of judgment, as the Lord commanded Moses.
verses.verse_html: 11And if his father have no brethren, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his kinsman that is next to him of his family, and he shall possess it: and it shall be unto the children of Israel a statute of judgment, as the Lord commanded Moses.

verses.text_plain: And the Lord said unto Moses, Get thee up into this mount Abarim, and see the land which I have given unto the children of Israel.
verses.verse_html: 12And the Lord said unto Moses, Get thee up into this mount Abarim, and see the land which I have given unto the children of Israel.

verses.text_plain: And when thou hast seen it, thou also shalt be gathered unto thy people, as Aaron thy brother was gathered.
verses.verse_html: 13And when thou hast seen it, thou also shalt be gathered unto thy people, as Aaron thy brother was gathered.

tokens.text: it, thou also shalt be gathered

verses.text_plain: For ye rebelled against my commandment in the desert of Zin, in the strife of the congregation, to sanctify me at the water before their eyes: that is the water of Meribah in Kadesh in the wilderness of Zin.
verses.verse_html: 14For ye rebelled against my commandment in the desert of Zin, in the strife of the congregation, to sanctify me at the water before their eyes: that is the water of Meribah in Kadesh in the wilderness of Zin.

verses.text_plain: And Moses spake unto the Lord, saying,
verses.verse_html: 15And Moses spake unto the Lord, saying,

verses.text_plain: Let the Lord, the God of the spirits of all flesh, set a man over the congregation,
verses.verse_html: 16Let the Lord, the God of the spirits of all flesh, set a man over the congregation,

verses.text_plain: Which may go out before them, and which may go in before them, and which may lead them out, and which may bring them in; that the congregation of the Lord be not as sheep which have no shepherd.
verses.verse_html: 17Which may go out before them, and which may go in before them, and which may lead them out, and which may bring them in; that the congregation of the Lord be not as sheep which have no shepherd.

verses.text_plain: And the Lord said unto Moses, Take thee Joshua the son of Nun, a man in whom is the spirit, and lay thine hand upon him;
verses.verse_html: 18And the Lord said unto Moses, Take thee Joshua the son of Nun, a man in whom is the spirit, and lay thine hand upon him;

verses.text_plain: And set him before Eleazar the priest, and before all the congregation; and give him a charge in their sight.
verses.verse_html: 19And set him before Eleazar the priest, and before all the congregation; and give him a charge in their sight.

verses.text_plain: And thou shalt put some of thine honour upon him, that all the congregation of the children of Israel may be obedient.
